item.title: Prayer bpn12442 in Namibia
item.description: Opena ou handulu oku ku fapo omaudyu ponhele ya Kalunga? Tya: Na hambelelwe Kalunga! Oye Kalunga! Aveshe ovapiya vaYe, ndele aveshe ohava dulika komhango yaYe! (Source category: Oshikwanyama : EKWAFO) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12442)
